  "bodyText": "The Corporate Affairs and Intellectual Property Office is to provide and maintain within the framework of the law and the available resources, a reliable system of public records and an efficient registry service which supports the commercial activities of the public and private sectors as well as the development of Barbados' domestic and international trade and business.\n\n## Directory\n\n| Role | Telephone |\n| --- | --- |\n| General | (246) 535-2401 |\n| General | (246) 535-2402 |\n| General | (246) 535-2404 |\n| Registrar | (246) 535-2402 |\n| Deputy Registrar, Companies | (246) 535-2405 |\n| Deputy Registrar, Copyright | (246) 535-2404 |\n| Deputy Registrar, Intellectual Property | (246) 535-2403 |\n| Assistant Registrar, Companies | (246) 535-2420 |\n| Assistant Registrar, Companies | (246) 535-2421 |\n| Corporate Affairs Officer, Companies | (246) 535-2421 |\n| Corporate Affairs Officer, Intellectual Property | (246) 535-2413 |\n| Legal Examiner, Intellectual Property | (246) 535-2406 |\n| Executive Secretary | (246) 535-2407 |\n| Assistant Accountant | (246) 535-2409 |\n| Senior Clerk | (246) 535-2408 |\n| Network Systems Administrator | (246) 535-2411 |\n| Systems Analyst | (246) 535-2412 |"
